{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They smashed the babies with their-- with their arms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These are not our defendants, who were refined men, and I'm sure wouldn't have done that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But our refined men were behind these people, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was real brutality, but it didn't seem to affect them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was their duty-- they had run out of their other munitions, and they had to do their quota.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A baby couldn't do any work building a road or anything, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That, I found the most shocking thing I ever saw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was testimony in the trial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We found a very interesting document in the course of this trial called the 'Endlosung.' That means the final solution.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was a group of what we Washingtonians-- I guess the Germans probably said the same word for it-- interdepartmental meeting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Justice Department, the Foreign Office-- about 14 of these interdepartmental officials, their top dogs-- went to a meeting under the auspices of the SS on January 20, 1942, and had a meeting so that Heydrich, who was given by Goering-- Goering was not innocent but didn't do any of this, gave it to Heydrich to do.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Heydrich called this meeting, and all of the officials, the top dogs-- maybe there were, I don't know how many people were there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Were there 20 people there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The document is available.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- he told them how it was going to be, that they were going to gather all the Jews from throughout Europe, comb through Europe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a well-known document by now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's 15 pages long, and I translated it originally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kempner wanted it quickly, and I translated it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was hard to translate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very rough German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was strange German.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
